[Michigan has had tuberculosis problems in cattle and deer for
several years. They are currently on a split state status with regard
to TB. (See:
<http://www.michigan.gov/mda/0,1607,7-125-2961_6860_24288---,00.html>)
For more detailed information on bovine tuberculosis readers are
encouraged to see the moderator's comments on ProMED-mail post
20100325.0948. - Mod.TG]

